<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10550087>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–10. Adults of Nephelobotys spp. 1 N. apiculata sp. nov., holotype, male (Yunnan). 2 N. habisalis, male (Guangxi). 3 N. nephelistalis, male (Zhejiang). 4 N. evenoralis, male (Hunan). 5 N. denticulatus, male (Guangxi). 6 N. semicircularis sp. nov., paratype, male (Yunnan). 7 N. brevis sp. nov., paratype, male (Guangdong). 8–10 N. flavicilialis, male (8–9 Yunnan, 10 Sichuan). Scale bars: 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10550087/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10550104>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–18. Male genitalia of Nephelobotys spp. 17 N. brevis sp. nov., paratype, Yunnan (genitalia slide No. SYSU0714). 18 N. flavicilialis, Yunnan (genitalia slide No. SYSU0719). a Whole genitalia. b Enlarged detail of base part of valva." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10550104/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10550116>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23–24. Female genitalia of Nephelobotys spp. 23 N. semicircularis sp. nov., paratype, Yunnan (genitalia slide No. SYSU0779). 24 N. brevis sp. nov., paratype, Guangdong (genitalia slide No. SYSU0791)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10550116/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

